topics.body:
Also more cute animal stories. Back at my old school we had an animal lab where you'd get to look at the animals they had there.

They had a Rabbit there. And they let us hold him.

Literally, every kid that got to hold him the Rabbit would be jumping around and want to leave.

I get to hold the Rabbit. Nothing. Absolutely nothing. All he did was laz around in my arms and do nothing.

All the other kids were like "....H-How?"

So apparently shits going down between Liberals and Progressives in the usa.

To use a metaphor you know how for Republicans there was a fight between RINO's and conservatives and it metaphorically ended cause conservatives are un-electable as presidential candidates?  Well that's seems to be happening to the left as well now, but not such a degree.  On the one side there's Bernie Sanders supporters; on the other there's Hillary supporters.

The thing is though yes I agree Hillary isn't that great of a candidate, *BUT* she is electable.
